  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "You've never experienced anything like the incredible action of MONSTER TRUCK RALLY! Compete against the computer - or against up to three of your friends at once - in nine grueling, gear-grinding events: hill climb, drag race, car crush, sled pull, monster rally, drawbridge, donuts, tug-o-war, and bog! Whether you build your own custom course, or have the computer build one for you randomly - out of millions of possible combinations - every event is sure to be an awesome new challenge, every time!",
